  "detailed_description": "参加游戏讨论、获取攻略等，欢迎加入<strong>官方玩家群</strong>：611630436<br><strong>无剧透攻略</strong>：<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2098070/extras/0d0b84a06ec3f4ce6e2114a3f39e8184.webp?t=1733037415\" width=480 height=54 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>欢迎来到演艺圈首屈一指的高等学府——星之诗学院！<br></li><li>扮演初出茅庐的新秀\"艾丽\"，在三年的求学中，磨练技艺，踏上星途。<br></li><li>愉快多彩的校园生活，前途无量的职业发展，酸甜苦辣的爱情，温暖心灵的友情——我全都要！<br></li><li>近百张CG，百万字剧本，丰富的游戏系统<br></li><li>七位可攻略角色，五位友情角色，均有专属故事路线和CG<br></li><li>可选九种职业路线，数百种通告，从台前到幕后，一切皆有可能</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2098070/extras/bb5def885bf7f9e945769a8933a15b64.webp?t=1733037415\" width=480 height=54 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2098070/extras/b4eed052dcba2702c4bb4c39850714f6.avif?t=1733037415\" width=600 height=800 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2098070/extras/1f88d5d9bcd3c3bd0724664e9ed7a94e.avif?t=1733037415\" width=600 height=798 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2098070/extras/668f4dd38a89e5f65163875159415ec9.avif?t=1733037415\" width=600 height=798 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2098070/extras/223222d9f141c54209bb9ce950323231.avif?t=1733037415\" width=600 height=798 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2098070/extras/a9443b692f76bb941695b43887050b92.avif?t=1733037415\" width=600 height=798 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2098070/extras/89ee34a5e6b5af2777a3b3eb2e526fae.avif?t=1733037415\" width=600 height=798 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2098070/extras/c3bca5d81d9faacf6a68e8cc75f6bbf3.avif?t=1733037415\" width=600 height=798 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2098070/extras/8b4f467d4b22f576166d4d384d79d48d.avif?t=1733037415\" width=600 height=798 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2098070/extras/d580c2a05b4dd5f82f1e4fe94465dab6.webp?t=1733037415\" width=480 height=54 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>繁华的架空都市S城，在这里坐落着演艺圈的梦工厂——星之诗学院。光是拿到入学资格就令无数心怀明星梦的考生艳羡，要想成功毕业，更是难上加难。<br></li><li>为了追求梦想，远离家乡和父母，独自一人踏入星之诗的少女，将会谱写怎样的未来呢？</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2098070/extras/a6ae0d1c455c51456faf854ebf0b7e78.webp?t=1733037415\" width=480 height=54 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>日程：当卷王还是摸鱼？——经典的模拟养成游戏模式，自由安排每天的活动<br></li><li>换装：近30套可收集服装，随心更换，在关键的场合或赴约会时换上合适的服装，也许会有惊喜<br></li><li>道具：提升能力的消耗品，赠送朋友或恋人的礼物，逛商店也是努力的一环？——当然！<br></li><li>社交：三人行必有我师，追求理想怎能少了贵人相助？结识同学前辈、当红明星，各领域的专家，联络感情的同时还能提升实力<br></li><li>情报：伴随剧情发展，游戏内的SNS“飞特”将会不断更新，想看到最新的八卦资讯？自己接下的通告，得到了粉丝怎样的评价？记得时不时关注一下哦！</li></ul>",
